{\listtext	\'95	}1 (15-ounce) can cherries (sweet in light syrup)\
{\listtext	\'95	}1 tablespoon chipotle paste, or pureed chipotle with a little {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/adobo-sauce/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 adobo sauce}}\
{\listtext	\'95	}1 tablespoon molasses\
{\listtext	\'95	}Salt and freshly ground black pepper\
